 This Agreement for Judgment should be used by a Creditor with a Debtor after the Default date under a note has passed.  The Creditor benefits by getting the Debtor to waive any contest of the note; the Debtor gains by getting an extention of the 
collection process; both parties win by cutting down on their legal expenses.
