ioned Debtor by providing more time; it assists the Creditor by eliminating legal hurdles to perfecting their interests in the assets of the Debtor.
\par 
\par If the Debtor will not sign the Agreement, then move instantly to formal foreclosure for judgment in the appropriate court of law.  You should seek legal counsel to execute these tasks and assist in collecting the outstanding judgment, i
nterest, and legal costs due under the original note.
